Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是与我紧紧地缠绕的话不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.60,0:22:38.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.56,0:22:49.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.82,0:22:55.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.17,0:23:08.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.02,0:23:19.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.77,0:23:27.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能  太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.15,0:23:33.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.57,0:23:44.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.57,0:00:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会有很多警察先生出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探团也一起做推理立功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.31,0:00:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.77,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本厅刑警恋爱物语2(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经有一点察觉到你的真面目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.82,0:01:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么继续隐藏下去也没有意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.66,0:01:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会伤害她而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要告诉我这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.47,0:02:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够看透邪恶的你这双正义之眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不能明白女人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从第一次见面之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.46,0:02:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你并没有发觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.35,0:02:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡！卡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要表现得更加惊讶一点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一幕是背叛黑道的女间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.89,0:02:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对假面超人告白的一个冲击的场面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是学艺祭要表演的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样应该做些更加平常的戏剧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.96,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如桃太郎或者是一休和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.68,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么荒谬的故事 我办不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人不是也差不多吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.01,0:02:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是委屈求全扮演大番薯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别那么多牢骚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.67,0:02:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地为了让大家感受到真正的现场环境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.27,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地跑到废弃大厦里面来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.94,0:03:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样不如演警察故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种故事不是常常出现吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察进入废弃大厦时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧遇见强盗的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起双手 不要乱动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.09,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.52,0:03:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啊 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.58,0:03:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跑到顶楼去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木 你从下面追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被已逮捕的犯人给脱逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要把他带回总部的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了机车和卡车相撞事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.39,0:05:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人趁我不注意的时候偷偷地跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他看起来很老实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根本没想过他会逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.14,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真粗心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的被逃走的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去不是写报告就可以了事的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18点43分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将逃亡中的犯人逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手铐的链子断掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要给人添麻烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是掉在哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不要这么莽撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有杀人 警察小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才上面是不是有什么奇怪的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太多疑了吧？ 上面全都上锁了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶快把工作做完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.64,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是美术馆吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么一幅画也没有呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是正在更换作品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.03,0:07:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说很危险要你们赶快回家去的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木 我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里 佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 这里可是男厕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那个逃犯怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓是抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.62,0:07:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过却出了点意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按常理手铐应该是铐在犯人的双手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不想让他再跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就铐到自己的手上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.78,0:07:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像弄丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被一课的人知道的话会很丢脸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不可以偷偷帮我拿备用钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能偷偷地呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为犯人逃走现在大家都很紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对前辈竟然讲这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是你不小心看守让犯人给逃掉的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是这样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜托你了 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过早上我醒来之后村西小姐就已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从刚才就一直这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 请相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 东田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是和你住在同一座公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.72,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你公司的上司村西真美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡现场是她的房间的浴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而当发现她死亡的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正喝醉酒睡在她的床上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的门锁也是用门链锁上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以房间是个密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.18,0:08:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房间的钥匙还有门链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有绕在死者脖子的三色电线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有你的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.73,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你在工作上常常和她起争吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天你不是和她在酒吧里面吵了一架吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们只能认为是你跑到她的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.46,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用电线杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.87,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上锁是为了不让她逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在杀害她之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为喝醉所以就睡在她的床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一点印象都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说是因为你酒后杀人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.84,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确因为她在工作上常找我麻烦让我很恨她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我却没有恨到要杀她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你为什么要逃呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.91,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有个地方必须去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到加拿大的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.52,0:09:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我离婚后让太太抚养的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要结婚的喜帖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为她这17年来一直恨着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我有理由不去参加吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.79,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到我的房间去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以看到我女儿写给我的信和飞机票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大叔不是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这位大叔放了步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还向我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是坏人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会这样做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明天几点的飞机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成田机场12点30分出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意照我的话去做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.43,0:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 联络不到佐藤和高木？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才就一直打他们的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是追踪犯人中发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找 他们二人应该还在那附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鸟 我们也过去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天12点前要找到真正犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我会好好看着他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这种样子也无法行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我去拿钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带回警署然后我们再…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果回警署拿钥匙被发现的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被上级知道的话就太丢脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在写报告的时候 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机早就飞走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听着 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.90,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就假装我们现在正在寻找逃走的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去找出真正的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫌犯被移送检察署之前 如果已经证明他的清白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们警察就可以决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.70,0:11:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在移送之前就直接释放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后期限就是这间美术馆开馆的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上10点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有客人进入这个厕所的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候也会通知警方过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我愿意相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就我一个人实在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不是一个人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像很有干劲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 最后期限是明天早上10点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前你要找出真正的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明他是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你一定办得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信自己的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊 要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.82,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官的心上人不是目暮警官吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些话是为了让我增加信心而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从刚才就一下子兴奋一下子失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这楼梯下面不是有写着吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「禁止进入」的标志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发生了紧急状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.49,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们大家在追犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么犯人 你们又不是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.91,0:13:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 其实我是警视厅的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 逃亡中的这个嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我警察的身份被发现的话行动就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让他能赶得及参加她女儿的婚礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须秘密的自己去做调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在玩警察游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.63,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.92,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.05,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个警察好像很靠不住的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地善良又容易做错事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那种不能放心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在紧急时刻也会很努力去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.18,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也在身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个戴眼镜的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子总是很令人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第5辆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事情了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.47,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说他们是在找犯人和我和佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木刑事好像杀手一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.48,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 要做秘密调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 首先要先调查那间店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.73,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东田先生在案发前最后去过的那间居酒屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝得烂醉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今天一定要打死那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想不到东田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的做了那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一个人回去的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和他一起喝酒的北川先生一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二个人一起走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和东田先生是同一个公司的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.94,0:14:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就是他了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个发现尸体的北川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个发现者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.45,0:15:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案发隔日因为东田先生和村西小姐没上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他拜托管理员帮忙开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就在那里发现了尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱我放在桌子上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是警察 有几件事情想请问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说的我都已经向警察说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上司被朋友给杀害 我也很受打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请暂时让我自己冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 他已经在警局录了口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.77,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的居酒屋老板也被问过很多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.70,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 北川先生是东京Spirits的球迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东田先生是反东京Spirits的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在问些什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我们要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打电话回家 妈妈会担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.91,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.03,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样怎么可能在明天中午之前找到真正的犯人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说你们大家今天都要住在我这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们和高木警官一起我也很放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且明天是星期日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.98,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉他们你们在这里讨论该如何庆祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.91,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的发明终于可以贡献社会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我称做热带彩虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸时会有七色彩虹出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事情做完了 记得过来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士说可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.32,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是明天杯户镇会有个烟花大会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花 有这个庆祝节目吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.05,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 接下来就是案发现场村西小姐的房间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是警察啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.51,0:17:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午的警察先生们才刚走不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还有一些东西没有调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些小孩子们呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来做生活实习的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要看看警察先生的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到学校去做发表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～就像是「朝九晚五的叔叔」之类的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我等一下会把钥匙拿到管理室去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要乱碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才高木刑事在买帽子的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也买了这些手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南叫我们买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.55,0:17:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯、佐藤跟高木他们到底到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.76,0:17:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们追嫌犯到杯户镇的废弃大楼内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就失去联络了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官竟然几个小时都没有联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个人都落到了嫌犯手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对我重要的部下出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 嫌犯将佐藤给…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美和子被软禁了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 感冒了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.73,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为我让你着凉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的抓错人该道歉的人应该是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.93,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不是为了你而做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.32,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想让你女儿和我有同样不好的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.23,0:18:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候就失去父亲的那种寂寞感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么找也找不到什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查人员进来的时候地板一点毛发也没有发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的有四个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.30,0:19:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是枕头 棉被 床单还有窗帘的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.64,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房的厨具餐具还有装潢全部都是米黄色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.65,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有床和窗帘是灰色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.79,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这只是碰巧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.19,0:19:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过米黄色的窗帘和床单都在衣柜里面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且居酒屋的老板娘讲过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村西小姐最喜欢米黄色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还喜欢东京Spirits跟仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.14,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后东田先生对视听器材很详细却讨厌洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉之后就会不省人事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常早上上班都会迟到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事在录口供的时候都没有讲过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为警方录口供的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲一些与事件无关的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能会被责备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以经常会只讲重点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.88,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别看她那样子 那个老板娘很八卦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八卦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个就是不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拿掉的床边的月历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这是在柜子里面拿出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京spirits这个月的月历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.39,0:20:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和后面的日晒痕迹刚好一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是因为最近球队没发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会把它拿下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12月份的预定事务都写在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三就是家具有被移动过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点调查的人员也讲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是家具更换吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在移动衣柜的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.33,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没发觉到将这么重要的东西掉到柜子底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是一个普通的火柴盒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打开看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有一张纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村西小姐的结婚申请书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.59,0:21:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她是准备结婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过男方的名字却没有写
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面却已经盖了章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四是仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.64,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案发当日早上下了一些雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢仙人掌的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让仙人掌就这样放在外面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 除了她之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁不知道为了什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将许多东西给移动过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案发当日的傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘送给她的礼物 圆球仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过上面的针叶断掉了 真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这又能证明什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯的东田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.69,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天把这里当作自己的房间睡在床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是凶器的三色电线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.47,0:21:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的锁 还有门链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有东田先生的…指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这个房间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要不要去看看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.00,0:22:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的房间也在这栋公寓里吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.88,0:22:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.09,0:23:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.14,0:23:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我们快点进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.17,0:23:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个真正犯人的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.12,0:23:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的他说什么来着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.68,0:23:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是炸弹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.24,0:24:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.30,0:24:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.10,0:24:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.28,0:24:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.27,0:24:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.32,0:24:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.82,0:24:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.39,0:24:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本厅刑事恋爱物语2(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.24,0:24:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.77,0:24:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.43,0:24:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回刑事的恋爱有结果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.31,0:24:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的是和目暮警官
